These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Movie-Genre: scientific, time-travel, sports, crime
Cigar: pall-mall, tiparillo, cain, aristoff
1. Cigar:aristoff is on the left of Movie-Genre:sports##1
2. Movie-Genre:scientific is on the left of Cigar:tiparillo##1
3. Movie-Genre:crime is in an odd position##4
4. Cigar:cain is on the left or right of Cigar:aristoff##3
5. Movie-Genre:scientific is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | time-travel | crime | sports |
| Cigar        | pall-mall | tiparillo   | aristoff | cain    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Cigar: game, cain, bluemaster, bolivar
Music-Genre: blues, house, hip-hop, classical
1. Cigar:cain is on the left of Cigar:bolivar##1
2. Music-Genre:blues is on the left of Music-Genre:hip-hop##1
3. Music-Genre:hip-hop is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:blues == Cigar:game##1
5. Music-Genre:house is on the right of Music-Genre:hip-hop##1
6. Music-Genre:blues == Cigar:game##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | game  | cain  | bolivar |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | blues | hip-hop | house    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
