Transport: train, skateboard, boat, roller
1. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Transport:roller##3
2. Cigar:aristoff is in an even position##4
3. Transport:roller is on the left or right of Cigar:dannemann##3
4. Transport:roller is on the right of Transport:boat##1
5. Transport:train is in an odd position##4
6. Cigar:dannemann is on the right of Cigar:aristoff##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Cigar          | blend | aristoff | dannemann    | bongani      |
| Transport   | boat        | roller     | train | skateboard |

