.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Game: whist, backgammon, chess, scrabble
Beverage: milk, coffee, mirinda, iced-tea
1. Game:backgammon is between Beverage:milk and Beverage:iced-tea##2
2. Game:scrabble is on the left of Game:whist##1
3. Beverage:mirinda is in an odd position##4
4. Beverage:coffee is on the left of Beverage:iced-tea##1
5. Beverage:coffee is on the right of Game:whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Game         | scrabble | whist | backgammon | chess |
| Beverage   | mirinda       | milk   | coffee    | iced-tea  |

