.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
City: boston, paris, venice, miami
Pet: horse, bird, snake, pony
1. City:venice is on the right of Pet:pony##1
2. Pet:bird == City:miami##1
3. Pet:snake is on the right of City:boston##1
4. City:paris is on the far left##1
5. City:venice is in an odd position##4
6. Pet:horse is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| City   | paris  | boston    | venice   | miami       |
| Pet   | horse | pony | snake | bird |

