4. Birthday:may is on the right of House:futuristic##1
5. Birthday:august is between Birthday:may and Birthday:november##2
6. House:farmhouse is in an odd position##4
7. House:farmhouse is between Birthday:august and House:craftsman##2
8. Birthday:august is on the left or right of Birthday:november##3

